<P> <P><b><i>
<font face="Georgia" size="4" color="#9F3215">
Milo Says:
</font></i></b><BR>


   The minimum requirements for the game are as follows:<P>

   Windows 95/98/2000<BR>
   Pentium 200 w/ 64 MB of RAM<BR>
   600MB of hard drive space<BR>
   Internet connection (28.8Kbps minimum transfer rate)<BR>
   CD-ROM drive<BR>
   3D Accelerator card with at least 8MB of RAM<P>

   Take this information and go from there.  I play on an antediluvian
setup, at home: 400MHz Pentium II with two Monster II 3D cards.
The game ran great for me before I installed the Kunark expansion,
which I have yet to play.<P>

